net.sf.JRecord.CsvParser

Class BasicCsvByteLineParserExtended

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.JRecord.CsvParser.BaseCsvByteLineParser
      • net.sf.JRecord.CsvParser.BasicCsvByteLineParserExtended
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICsvByteLineParser

    public final class BasicCsvByteLineParserExtended
extends BaseCsvByteLineParser
    Basic CSV line parser. Basically - If the Field start with {Quote}; the fields is ended by {Quote}{Field-Seperator} - Otherwise the field ends with a {Field-Seperator}
    Warning - This class must be kept in sync with BasicCsvLineParserExtended class
    Author:
    Bruce Martin
    See Also:
